 Segun Olaniyan Katsina – Governor Aminu Bello Masari of Katsina state has approved the re-appointment of Alhaji Mustapha Muhammad Inuwa as the Secretary to the Government of the state. Similarly, Alhaji Muntari Lawal and Abdu Labaran Malumfashi have also been re-appointment as Permanent Secretary, Government house and Senior Special Assistant on Media respectively. In a statement made available and signed by Falalu Bawale, Director Administration, Government house katsina, the trio whose appointment takes immediate effect was in recognition of their dedication and commitment to the service of the state. Details later… The post Masari Re-appoints SGS, 2 Others In Katsina Source: Independent